description:
Track Ralph progress on remote VMs via Beads polling.

## Challenge
Can't use OpenCode session status (Ralph is shell script, not session).

## Solution
Poll Beads directly (works locally or remotely):
```python
def get_session_status(self, session_id: str) -> SessionInfo:
    # session_id = beads_id
    epic = bd.show(session_id, remote=True)  # Query remote Beads
    status = epic.get("status")

    if status == "closed":
        return SessionInfo(status=SessionStatus.COMPLETED)
    elif is_stale(epic.get("last_updated")):
        return SessionInfo(status=SessionStatus.STALE)
    else:
        return SessionInfo(status=SessionStatus.RUNNING)
```

